Package: seg
Version: 0.5-1
Date: 2014-5-28
Title: A set of tools for measuring spatial segregation
Authors@R: c(person("Seong-Yun", "Hong", role = c("aut", "cre"), email
        = "hong.seongyun@gmail.com"), person("David", "O'Sullivan",
        role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Seong-Yun Hong <hong.seongyun@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), methods, stats, sp
Imports: splancs
Suggests: spdep, spgrass6, rgdal
Description: A package that provides functions for measuring spatial 
        segregation. The methods implemented in this package include 
        White's P index (1983), Morrill's D(adj) (1991), Wong's D(w)
        and D(s) (1993), and Reardon and O'Sullivan's set of spatial 
        segregation measures (2004).
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://sites.google.com/site/hongseongyun/seg
        